Kemin Europa is a member of a number of European and National trade associations related to the product areas in which it operates.&#xd;
&#xd;
- FEFANA (EU Association of Specialty Feed Ingredients and their Mixtures)&#xd;
- FEFAC (European Feed Manufacturers' Federation)&#xd;
- FRANA (Belgium): Federatie van fabrikanten en vertegenwoordigers van toevoegingen voor dierlijke voeding/ Federation of manufacturers and representatives of animal feed additives&#xd;
- AWT (Germany): Arbeitsgemeinschaft für Wirkstoffe in der Tierernährung /Association for active ingredients in animal nutrition&#xd;
- BAFSAM (UK): British Association of Feed Supplement and Additive Manufacturers&#xd;
- VDDN (the Netherlands):  Branchevereniging voor producenten, importeurs en leveranciers van diervoederspecialiteiten en diergezondheidsproducten in Nederland / Trade Association for manufacturers, importers and suppliers of animal feed specialties in the Netherlands&#xd;
- BFA (Belgium): Belgian Feed Association (BFA)
